snippet.title: JIND MAHIYA: Pooh In Korea & Pravisht Mishra | Saaj Bhatt & Bhaswati Sengupta | Amjad Nadeem Aamir
snippet.description:
Voilà! Digi presents 'Jind Mahiya', the super awaited song starring Pooh In Korea & Pravisht Mishra and sung by Saaj Bhatt & Bhaswati Sengupta. This song is about a couple celebrating their 5 year relationship anniversary, where the guy decides to surprise his girl with 5 surprises, one for each year of their relationship. This is the fourth song from Saaj Bhatt's album, 'Jannatein'. #poohinkorea #pravishtmishra #saajbhatt #bhaswatisengupta #voiladigi

snippet.title: Practice Match 1 | SRH | IPL 2023
snippet.description:
Two teams - Brook XI & Bhuvi XI battle it out in a practice match comprising of 20 overs!

Brook XI ends up with a team score of 212/3. Bhuvi XI manages to score 195/7 thus gifting us an absolute entertainer in our first practice match

snippet.title: Jetha और Bagha ने क्यों खिलाए Mahila मंडल को समोसे? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Mahila Mandal comes to Jethalal and speaks about Daya. They all say that they miss Daya as Navratri is almost here. Speak of that Jethalal becomes emotional and he goes back home. He has a nostalgic evening. Stay tuned.   

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonyliv 

Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

#tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah 

Click here to watch all the funny videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLn5vww_8o5KuK429Bq2LJNS-l0Fegg9lw

snippet.title: Harrdy Sandhu - Yaad Aati Hai ft. Abhishek Singh | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira
snippet.description:
Harrdy Sandhu is back on Desi Melodies with ‘Yaad Aati Hai’. Written and composed by Jaani, this soulful ode to lost love and memories is elevated by Hunny Bunny's evocative music production. The short film, directed by Arvindr Khaira, features Abhishek Singh and Asmita Sood, who bring to life the emotions of Harrdy’s voice with their soul-stirring performances. 

Listen to ‘Yaad Aati Hai’ on your favourite streaming platform - https://umgindia.lnk.to/YAH

This Odia Music Video " Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora " Is Directed By Somio R , Penned By Panchanan Nayak And Music By Your All Time Favorite Japani Bhai .Please Enjoy And Share Rupa & Pintu New Odia Album Song " Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora " . Starring - Rupa & Pintu

"Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora"
Lyrics:-

Mukhuda:-
**************
M:-
Aji phagunare lagigala ranga
              Sei ranga aji deigala daga

Cross:-
Hrudaya jadi delu tu mate
       De kahile debi mu tate, tope sindura

Tag:-
F:-
Mu heigali heigali heigali heigali
                 Ajithu tora.....(୦)
M:-
Tu heigalu heigalu heigalu heigalu 
                 Ajithu mora.....(୦)



Antara:-01
***************
M:-
Piladine gote kahani te sunithili
       Aakasha deshare pari tie thae boli
           Tu sei pari, aji janigali

F:-
Kebe dine gote kabita te padhithili
         Sagara majhire raja tie rahe boli
               Tu sei raja, aji chinhi gali

Cross:-
M:-
Chhatire tate rakhibaa pain
        Sata sagara asichi dein, debi sindura

Tag:-
F:-
Mu heigali heigali heigali heigali
                 Ajithu tora.....(01)
M:-
Tu heigalu heigalu heigalu heigalu
                 Ajithu mora.....(01)

Antara:-02
**************
F:-
Dinaku dina mu saja hue beshi kain 
   Aina kahuchi to pari sundari nahi
           Mu bodhe to bata, rahichi chahi

M:-
Aakasha taa aji pruthibi ku chhuindela
      Nijathu nijara kehi jane miligala
            To bata mo bata, gotie hela

Cross:-
F:-
 Manaku gote mana milila
      Aau ja khali baki rahila, tope sindura

Tag:-
M:-
Mu heigali heigali heigali heigali
                 Ajithu tora.....(02)
F:-
Tu heigalu heigalu heigalu heigalu 
                 Ajithu mora.....(02)

snippet.title: “लड़कों ने मुझसे दूर रहना शुरू कर दिया था” | @elladverma622 | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Ella जी की तरह आप भी करे अपने सपने सच: https://joshskills.app.link/1tWjLnYpqyb

Ella D' Verma is a Model. She is going to represent Delhi in the upcoming competition of Miss Trans queen. Her life story has never been easy, since childhood she was fond of living like a girl but society made her fun because she was a boy at that time. Today she is a successful model and has emerged as an inspiration for us.

Today Ella D' Verma will tell her story through Josh Talks, listening to which you too will get the courage to achieve your goals. So definitely watch this Hindi motivational/inspirational video of Josh Talks.

Ella D' Verma एक Model हैं और Miss Trans queen के होने वाले Competition में Delhi को represent करने वाली हैं. इनकी Life story कभी आसान नहीं रही, बचपन से इन्हें लड़कियों की तरह रहने का शौक था लेकिन समाज में इनका बहुत मज़ाक उड़ाया जाता था. आज ये एक Successful Model हैं और हमारे लिए एक Inspiration की तरह उभर कर सामने आई हैं. 

आज जोश Talks के माध्यम से Ella D' Verma अपनी कहानी बताएंगी जिसे सुनकर आपको भी अपने लक्ष्य हासिल करने का हौसला मिलेगा. तो जोश Talks की इस Hindi motivational/inspirational video को पूरा ज़रूर देखें.  

#JoshTalksHindi #EllaVermaJoshTalks #motivationalvideo #motivationalstory #motivationalspeech #model

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

► जोश Talks Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/JoshTalksHindi​ 
► जोश Talks Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/JoshTalksHi... 

DISCLAIMER -
All of the views and work outside the pretext of the video of the speaker, are his/ her own, and Josh Talks, by any means, does not support them directly or indirectly and neither is it liable for it. Viewers are requested to use their own discretion while viewing the content and focus on the entirety of the story rather than finding inferences in its parts. Josh Talks by any means, does not further or amplify any specific ideology or propaganda.

आज जोश Talks के माध्यम से Ella D' Verma अपनी कहानी बताएंगी जिसे सुनकर आपको भी अपने लक्ष्य हासिल करने का हौसला मिलेगा. तो जोश Talks की इस Hindi motivational/inspirational video को पूरा ज़रूर देखें.  

#JoshTalksHindi #EllaVermaJoshTalks #motivationalvideo #motivationalstory #motivationalspeech #model

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

snippet.description:

ख़रीदिए कारवाँ मोबाइल- 1500 प्रीलोडिड गानों वाला कीपैड फ़ोन धमाकेदार साउंड के साथ

🌈DI - Rohit Singh

Lyrics:

F तुम Attitude मेरे Mood को समझ ना पा ते हो
F तंग आ चुकी हूँ तुझसे तुम बड़ा सता ते हो
F तेरे चक्कर मे ना आउंगी रह लुंगी तेरे बिन
M मैं प्या र से बो लता हूँ तु बन जा ती ना गिन-2
================Music=============
F Boyfriend मेरे हो तुम नखड़े उठा ना पड़ेगा
F मैं जब बुला ऊंगी तुमको एक का ल पे आना पड़ेगा
M तेरे पा पा का मैं ना Servant हूँ
M मैं पढने ली खने वा ला Student हूँ
F चल हट में सा मने से ना मा र बा तो से पिन-2
M हम प्या र से बो लिला त तू बन जा लू ना गिन-2
================Music=============
F मेरी जैसी लड़की अर्जुन ईस जनम में ना मिलेगी
F फूल बन कर तेरे बा हो में को ई और ना खिलेगी
M तेरे का रन रहता हूँ मैं Dipration में
M तू डा ल देती है खेसा री को Tension में

F छो डूंगी पच्छा तो गे मैं हूँ छो री नमकी न
M मैं प्या र से बो लता हूँ तु बन जा ती ना गिन-2

mr.title: कांदे पोहे - कोथरूड VS सातारा । #Satara #Kothrud | #BhaDiPa
mr.description:
कोथरूडच्या आपल्या मुलीला बघायला आलंय रॉयल साताऱ्याचं स्थळ! कोथरुडकरांसाठी सातारा काही जास्त लांब नाही. ह्या वेळेस कांदेपोह्यांपासून सुरु झालेला कार्यक्रम कंदीपेढे खाऊन गोड होईल का? कोथरूड आणि सातारकरांची सोयरीक जुळेल का? जाणून घेण्यासाठी विडिओ शेवटपर्यंत पहा. 

कास्ट:
लीना भागवत
भाग्यश्री लिमये
रोहित माने
संतोष पाटील

श्रेयावली:
दिग्दर्शक - अक्षय नर
लेखक - सुमित पाटील
सिनेमॅटोग्राफर - अजिंक्य खडपेकर
ध्वनी - सनी
संकलक - करिष्मा दळवी
सहाय्यक दिग्दर्शक - सार्थक चिरनेरकर
कलरिस्ट - अजिंक्य खडपेकर
प्रोडक्शन हेड - केदार नायडू
प्रोडक्शन कॉर्डिनेटर  - अक्षय गोपाळ
प्रोग्रामिंग हेड आणि मार्केटिंग स्ट्रॅटेजिस्ट - प्राची हंकारे आणि अक्षय नर
क्रिएटिव्हस् - अनिकेत जाधव, नदीम खान

लाईट - किसन

snippet.title: മഴപെയ്യുമ്പോൾ ചളി നിറയുന്ന വീടായിരുന്നു എന്റേത് | @jasminjaffar | Josh Talks Malayalam
snippet.description:
ജീവിതത്തിൽ ഒരുപാട് വെല്ലുവിളികൾ നേരിട്ട് ഇന്ന് അറിയപ്പെടുന്ന ഒരു influencer ആയി സോഷ്യൽ മീഡിയയിൽ നിറഞ്ഞു നിൽക്കുന്ന ജാസ്മിൻ ജാഫർ അന്ന് ജോഷ് Talks ഇൽ  തനറെ ജീവിതകഥ പറയുന്നത്. 

ജാസ്മിൻ ജാഫർ തന്റെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ ഒരുപാട് വെല്ലുവിളികളും ബുദ്ധിമുട്ടുകളും തരണം ചെയ്ത് നിരവധി ആളുകൾക്ക് പ്രചോദനമായി മാറിയ സ്വാധീനശക്തിയാണ്. 

ജാസ്മിന്റെ ആദ്യകാല ജീവിതം നിരവധി പോരാട്ടങ്ങളും തിരിച്ചടികളും നിറഞ്ഞതായിരുന്നു. പരിമിതമായ സാമ്പത്തിക സ്രോതസ്സുള്ള ഒരു കുടുംബത്തിലാണ് അവൾ ജനിച്ച് വളർന്നത്, അവളുടെ മാതാപിതാക്കൾ പലപ്പോഴും ജീവിതത്തിന്റെ രണ്ടറ്റങ്ങളും കൂട്ടിമുട്ടിക്കാൻ കഷ്ടപെട്ടിരുന്നു.

ജാസ്മിൻ ജാഫർ അവിശ്വസനീയമാംവിധം സ്വാധീനിക്കുകയും ജീവിതത്തിൽ പോരാടുന്ന എല്ലാവർക്കും പ്രചോദനവുമാണ്. പോസിറ്റീവിറ്റി, സ്ഥിരോത്സാഹം, നിശ്ചയദാർഢ്യം എന്നിവയുടെ ശക്തിയുടെ തെളിവാണ് അവളുടെ കഥ, നമ്മൾ എന്ത് വെല്ലുവിളികൾ നേരിട്ടാലും, നമ്മുടെ ലക്ഷ്യങ്ങളിൽ പ്രതിജ്ഞാബദ്ധരായാൽ അവയെ തരണം ചെയ്യാനും നമ്മുടെ സ്വപ്നങ്ങൾ നേടാനും കഴിയുമെന്ന് ഇത് കാണിക്കുന്നു.

Jasmin Jaffer, who has faced a lot of challenges in her life and is a popular influencer on social media, tells her life story on Josh Talks.

Jasmine Jaffer is a remarkable force of influence who has overcome many challenges and hardships in her life and become an inspiration to many people. Jasmine's early life was filled with many struggles and setbacks. She was born and brought up in a family with limited financial resources and her parents often struggled to make ends meet.

Jasmine Jaffer is incredibly influential and an inspiration to everyone struggling in life. Her story is a testament to the power of positivity, perseverance and determination, and it shows that no matter what challenges we face, we can overcome them and achieve our dreams if we commit to our goals.

ഇപ്പോൾ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് Josh Talks വീഡിയോകളിൽ നിങ്ങളുടെ ബ്രാൻഡ് പ്രദർശിപ്പിക്കാനും പരസ്യം ചെയ്യാനും varun@joshtalks.com  ഇൽ Connect ചെയ്യൂ.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalis. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

ഊർജ്ജസ്വലരായ യുവജനങ്ങളുടെ കഴിവുകളെ പ്രോത്സാഹിപ്പിക്കുകയും, അവരുടെ ജീവിതത്തിൽ അവർ നേരിടുന്ന തിരിച്ചടികൾ മറികടക്കാൻ അവർക്ക് പ്രചോദനം നൽകുകയും ചെയ്യുക എന്നതാണ് ഞങ്ങളുടെ ലക്ഷ്യം. 

#joshtalksmalayalam  #motivation #nevergiveup

കേരളത്തിലെ ഏറ്റവും മികച്ച വാര്‍ത്താ നെറ്റ്‌വര്‍ക്കാണ് മീഡിയവണ്‍. മൂല്യാധിഷ്ഠിതവും സ്വതന്ത്രവുമായ മാധ്യമപ്രവർത്തനം നടത്തുന്ന മലയാള ന്യൂസ് ടെലിവിഷൻ ചാനലാണിത്‌. 24 മണിക്കൂറും ലോകത്തിന്‍റെ ഏത് ഭാഗത്ത് നിന്നും ഇവിടെ തത്സമയം കാണാം. അതിവേഗം വാര്‍ത്താ വീഡിയോകള്‍ ലഭിക്കാൻ മീഡിയവണ്‍ സബ്സ്ക്രൈബ് ചെയ്യാം.
സോഷ്യൽ മീഡിയ പ്ലാറ്റ്ഫോമുകളിലും മുൻനിരയിലാണ് മീഡിയവൺ.

snippet.title: Indians And Exercise | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys , 
Find your meaningful connection on happn : http://gethap.pn/aoHj

This Video shows all the crazy fun things that happens while exercising . Indians and Exercise we all have been there in different phases of our fitness journey incidents like  Single people going to gym , parks for workout , jog and suddenly meeting their love . Great for single guys and single girls for becoming fitness couple . Early morning walks with sister . Siblings going to parks like bonta , doing trekking and hiking , playing badminton . Enjoying healthy lifestyle coconut water with malai , vegetable juice , fruit juices , karela juice , chai tapri , tea and bread pakoda ,  eating neem leaves neem datun . Foodie Aunty going on diet to loose weight , controlling the urge to eating oily sugary atta halwa . Skipping sugar , oil , going on morning walks , avoiding cheat meals . Waking up early the 4 AM club to exercise . 2.0 version of friend she is so dedicated to change her body , workout clothes shopping , having every athletic brand nike addidas , puma , gym tights , sports bra , shoes , running , jogging , stretching and then workout motivation goes down in one day . Aunties Uncles laughing in park , joining free yoga classes . Girls and Girl things and their workout fashion . Yoga teacher frustrated with the class , helping the clients to loose weight , treat cervical , back pain , High Blood Pressure , doing pranayam , kapal bhati , yogasanas , aunty sleeping in shav asana and snoring , doing jel neti  , enjoying aerobics with friends , eating out after classes , so much more about the gym freaks , workout freaks , 
Do Share it with everyone, Comment your fav part and like krdena Video guys.. Subscribe the Channel for more amazing videos . 
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family  .. Comment down your Fav Part,

snippet.title: Rajya Sabha MPs Attack PM Modi, Shout Slogans: "Modi-Adani Bhai-Bhai"
snippet.description:
Opposition Protest in parliament: Taking a dig at Prime Minister Narendra Modi, the MPs in the Rajya Sabha shouted slogans "Modi-Adani Bhai-Bhai" on monday. In Lok Sabha, Congress leaders attended the session wearing black to protest against the disqualification of Rahul Gandhi. Lok Saha adjourned till 4pm today and Rajya Sabha adjourned till 2 pm. 

#parliamentprotest #rajyasabha #parliamentlive #rahulgandhi.

snippet.title: Trailer - Byomkesh O Pinjrapol (ব্যোমকেশ ও পিঁজরাপোল) | Anirban Bhattacharya | 7th April | hoichoi
snippet.description:
পিঁজরাপোল থেকে হাতছানি দিচ্ছে এক হাড়হিম করা রহস্য। প্রশ্ন একটাই - আমাদের সত্যান্বেষী কি এই তদন্তে হবে সফল?

Here's the official trailer of Byomkesh O Pinjrapol. Based on Sharadindu Bandyopadhyay's "Chiriyakhana", private detective Byomkesh Bakshi and his best friend and partner, author Ajit Kumar Banerjee embark upon a thrilling journey to uncover a spine-chilling mystery, where everyone is a suspect and truth has multiple faces! It even comments upon the psychology of our protagonist and shows a grey space between the black and white characters.

#ByomkeshOPinjrapol: Official Trailer | Series directed by Sudipto Roy, creative director Anirban Bhattacharya, premieres on 7th April, only on #hoichoi. 

Credits:

Cast: Anirban Bhattacharya, Ridhima Ghosh, Bhaswar Chatterjee, Babu Dutta Roy, Moitree Banerjee, Durbar Sharma, Anushka Chakraborty, Sampurnaa Mandal, Kaushik Hafizee, Dipanwita Sarkar, Soumik Maitra, Sanjay Paul, Susovon Guha, Sumanta Ray, Buddhadev Das, Manas Mukherjee
Director: Sudipto Roy

snippet.title: Minecraft Hostage Simulator
snippet.description:
Minecraft Hostage Simulator... this was the most ridiculous challenge we have ever done. It was absurd.

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dream
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dream

BadBoyHalo: @thesaintsofgames 
George: @GeorgeNotFound 
Sapnap: @Sapnap 

This video is a different Minecraft challenge concept that we have never done before!

In this challenge, BadBoyHalo is a hostage and we have to try and take him to the end portal. There are two teams, I am on one, and GeorgeNotFound & Sapnap are the other. BadBoyHalo can try and escape, but he can't break the rope that he's attached to.

It's a race, and it's super intense and we had a lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftChallenge

snippet.title: Naagin 6 | नागिन 6 | Ep. 117 | Meher Defends Prathna | Highlight
snippet.description:
Naagin 6 | नागिन 6 | Ep. 117 | Meher Defends Prathna | Highlight

Raghu gets the police to arrest Prathna for keeping Purvika with her. Meanwhile, Meher tries to defend Prathna against everyone and tells them how she saved Purvika's life. How will Prathna get out of this situation?

Prathna promises to cherish Purvika forever. Raghu demands that Prathna return Purvika and accuses her of bringing misfortune. However, Prathna binds Raghu in a Nagapaash and takes Purvika away. Will the estranged family ever reunite?

Naagin, the saga of love and revenge, sacrifice. This supernatural show traces the lives of 'ichchadhari' naagins. Watch on, as every season, the Naagin fights evil and keeps the ultimate source of power safe.

snippet.description:
Namaskaara Bossu, Dedicate this song to everyone who doubts you, critisice you in your journey,
1st they laugh,
next they talk,
at last you win ❤️
This is life ❤️

much love to all my fans, friends,media & memers who supported me since day 1 🙏🏻
love u all bossu ❤️

After the incredible success of his hit single "Don't Worry" in 2019, All Ok, the rising star of the music industry is making a grand return with "Don't Worry 2", which promises to offer a fresh perspective on All Ok's distinctive sound. 

With a combination of captivating beats and heartfelt lyrics, "Don't Worry 2" is sure to create an unforgettable listening experience. Get ready to groove and sing along with one of the most popular artists in the industry as he delivers another exciting new release.

snippet.title: India Travel Vlog in Tamil | Alandra's Adventure in India - Steffi Ulagam
snippet.description:
In this video, I am sharing some of the highlights from my recent trip to India. This was Alandra's second visit to India and this time, she had a lot of fun visiting the farm, beach, seeing all relatives and shopping. I was in India for 6 weeks and Alandra had a blast. She also had a lot of fun with cats and trying the different fruits there.
#steffiulagam #steffivlogs

Friends, hope you liked this week's vlog. While, I don't think I can do the weekly vlogs in Steffi Ulagam, I will occasionally share some of the events and interesting things in Madras Samayal. Thank you so much for your love and support.

------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: Chengiz Official Hindi Teaser | Jeet | Susmita | Rohit Roy | Shataf | Neeraj Pandey | Rajesh Ganguly
snippet.description:
‘Chengiz’ has officially set foot.
Get ready for an action-packed experience as we unveil the Hindi Teaser of #Chengiz. The story of an underworld don whose grip on the city is unbreakable. This is the very first time a Bengali film is set to release in Hindi simultaneously. So, mark your calendars and get ready to enter the dark, mysterious world of the underworld, with us!

Story : Neeraj Pandey & Rajesh Ganguly

snippet.title: మా పెద్దోడి చిన్నోడి పుట్టువెంట్రుకల వేడుక || Hair Tonsure Ceremony || @MANUCHERRY || Tamada Media
snippet.description:
Welcome to Manu & Cherry ! We're a family of four with two adorable sons, Happy and Richy. As parents and actors, we share our daily adventures and experiences with you. snippet.title: Why Rahul Gandhi was disqualified as Lok Sabha MP after conviction? IN NEWS | Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
Today’s InNews PDF Telegram Link: https://t.me/innewsdrishtiias

Why Rahul Gandhi was disqualified as Lok Sabha MP after conviction? 

Congress leader Rahul Gandhi has been disqualified from the Lok Sabha, a day after he was convicted in a defamation case by a Surat court. A notice issued by the Lok Sabha Secretariat said he stood disqualified from the House from March 23, the day of his conviction. Rahul Gandhi has to now move a higher court and get his conviction stayed. Chief Judicial Magistrate HH Verma convicted Gandhi in a 2019 defamation case, for saying ‘why do all thieves have the name Modi’, and sentenced him to two years in prison. The remarks were made during a rally in Kolar, Karnataka, in the run-up to the 2019 Lok Sabha elections. “Why do all thieves, be it Nirav Modi, Lalit Modi or Narendra Modi, have Modi in their names,” Gandhi had said in Hindi.

localized.title: Why Rahul Gandhi was disqualified as Lok Sabha MP after conviction? IN NEWS | Drishti IAS
localized.description:
Today’s InNews PDF Telegram Link: https://t.me/innewsdrishtiias

Why Rahul Gandhi was disqualified as Lok Sabha MP after conviction? 

Congress leader Rahul Gandhi has been disqualified from the Lok Sabha, a day after he was convicted in a defamation case by a Surat court. A notice issued by the Lok Sabha Secretariat said he stood disqualified from the House from March 23, the day of his conviction. Rahul Gandhi has to now move a higher court and get his conviction stayed. Chief Judicial Magistrate HH Verma convicted Gandhi in a 2019 defamation case, for saying ‘why do all thieves have the name Modi’, and sentenced him to two years in prison. The remarks were made during a rally in Kolar, Karnataka, in the run-up to the 2019 Lok Sabha elections. “Why do all thieves, be it Nirav Modi, Lalit Modi or Narendra Modi, have Modi in their names,” Gandhi had said in Hindi.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3728 - 25 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3728: Nayi Scheme
--------------------------------------------------------
Rustom the new area manager of Ramsang company plans to blacklist Gada Electronics for the unprofessional behavior of Jethalal as he was late to the meeting. Rustom tries to run from the Gada electronics, but Jetha chases him as he misunderstood him to be a thief. Later, Rustom meets Jethalal in his shop, where he explains the new scheme to him on account of the 25th year anniversary of the company. Watch the episode 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3728, 25 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000214716

snippet.title: *I FINALLY moved into my new apartment* 🏡 || VLOG
snippet.description:
Hello,
Last few days before we move into my new apartment...! It's been hectic, with the pregnancy and so many decisions to be taken, I'm just grateful to be healthy and waking up in my new house every day now. 

Can't wait to get back to normalcy and routine, I need to focus on the baby and my birth now.

Thank you for coming with me on this Journey, it's the end of an era but it's the beginning of a new book in my life. 
I love you
Xx

snippet.title: Naagin 6 | नागिन 6 | Ep. 116 | Highlight | Prathna Meets Raghu
snippet.description:
Naagin 6 | नागिन 6 | Ep. 116 | Highlight | Prathna Meets Raghu

As Prathna takes Mahakaali's forms, Raghu lies down on her feet to calm her. Prathna gets emotional seeing Prathna and blames him for taking her daughter away. Later, Prathna saves Meher's life. But will she be able to learn about her real identity?

Naagin, the saga of love and revenge, sacrifice. This supernatural show traces the lives of 'ichchadhari' naagins. Watch on, as every season, the Naagin fights evil and keeps the ultimate source of power safe.

snippet.description:

Tere Bin Episode 26 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 23rd March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Yumna Zaidi as Meerab

നമ്മളിൽ നിന്നും വ്യത്യസ്ത ചിന്തകളുമായി ജിവിക്കുന്ന ആളുകൾ നമ്മുടെ ചുറ്റുപാടും ഉണ്ടാകും അങ്ങനെ വേറിട്ടു ജീവിക്കുന്ന ആളുകളെ നിങ്ങൾക്ക് അറിയാമെങ്കിൽ അറിയിക്കാൻ മറക്കല്ലേ നിങ്ങളുടെയൊക്കെ സപ്പോർട്ട് ഉണ്ടെങ്കിൽ നമുക്ക് ഇവരെയൊക്കെ പുറംലോകത്തേക്ക് കൊണ്ടുവരാം.🥰

snippet.title: Naagin 6 | नागिन 6 | Ep. 116 | Highlight | Raghu Confronts Prathna
snippet.description:
Naagin 6 | नागिन 6 | Ep. 116 | Highlight | Raghu Confronts Prathna

Unknown to Purvika being her daughter, Prathna meets her and praises her. Later, Raghu confronts Prathna and asks about Purvika but lateral challenges him to find her. Will Prathna learn about Purvika's identity?

Naagin, the saga of love and revenge, sacrifice. This supernatural show traces the lives of 'ichchadhari' naagins. Watch on, as every season, the Naagin fights evil and keeps the ultimate source of power safe.
